<P>
   CABLE-SETTOPBOXES _ July 1 is the deadline for makers of cable
set top boxes to come out with a box that can be sold directly to
consumers in stores like Cirbuit City. This is government mandated
to try to foster competition in a market dominated by just two
players: Scientific Atlanta and General Instruments. But nobody
thinks consumers really want to buy set top boxes through retail
stores. (Brister, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 16.
</P>
