<P>
   COXNET WHEELS - (EDS: This is the CoxNet WHEELS page for the
current week. This layout is now available.)
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0624 -- The 2001 Acura 3.2CL Type S coupe is an
Acura that's going to astonish folks who aren't familiar with what
parent company Honda has been doing of late with its engines, which
benefit from trickledown technology from Formula One Grand Prix
