 (Three color slides are available.) 
 From WWD 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    Michael Kors is playing both sides of the net for resort. The
designer is volleying between ladylike looks with a hint of the
preppy for Collection, while for his bridge line, Kors, he's going
the super-sporty route. Both, however, still have a sexy edge.
