<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-27 20:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6573 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-WORLDLY-INVEST-NYT &LR;      06-27 0597
