   (UNDATED) _ America's quadrennial search for a designated
mourner at the funerals of foreign dignitaries _ otherwise known as
the vice president _ is in full swing. Short-lists are being drawn
up. Short-lists are being narrowed down... Is the veepstakes the
creation of bored pundits with too much time on their hands? Not
entirely. This time, there is a slim chance the choice of running
mate could actually make a difference. &QL;
